$AV_ADD3
## Action FMTADRPAY
Call FMTADRPAY([M]CRY) From TRTDIV
If GFMT<>""
 Chgfmt [M]ADD3(indice) With "K:"+GFMT
Else
 Chgfmt [M]ADD3(indice) With "-K:1X"
