$ON_TEL
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_TEL From W1HRMAT1
Onevent CONTROL Call C_TEL(zc) From W1HRMAT1
Onevent AFTER_CHANGE Gosub AMM_TEL From W1HRMAT1
Return

$AV_TEL
## Action FMTTELPAY
Call FMTTELPAY([M]CRY) From TRTDIV
